{"parentUuid":"d54de0a7-6863-4519-a074-b463ffd91ab6","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_017cct8iJqbpMgaGyjMy4HYV","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"For an MVP that's maximally useful without over-engineering:\n\n**Show calls only** — tool name + key inputs, skip results.\n\nReasons:\n- Tool results are often huge (file contents, search output) and dominate the file\n- The *interesting* thing for debugging is usually \"what did Claude decide to do?\" not the raw output\n- You can always add a `--verbose` flag later to include results\n\nSo the MVP output per turn would be:\n\n```\n## User — 12:24:03\nfor test purposes ask me a multiple choice question.\n\n## Assistant — 12:24:10\n> Tool: AskUserQuestion — \"What is the capital of France?\"\n\n## User — 12:24:20\n*(answered AskUserQuestion)*\n\n## Assistant — 12:24:23\nCorrect! Paris is the capital of France.\n```\n\nClean, skimmable, zero noise. Want to go with that?"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":3,"cache_creation_input_tokens":108,"cache_read_input_tokens":30294,"output_tokens":211,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":108,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CZTfhmU88WVbtmKbdj441","type":"assistant","uuid":"ef9f1f60-5a92-4367-bdc3-5f414a87a791","timestamp":"2026-03-27T13:31:46.078Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/robert.shankin/codingRepo/jsonl-reader","sessionId":"4812baa4-eab4-43d3-a58c-24d05ff631cd","version":"2.1.85","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"eager-inventing-shore"}
