{"parentUuid":"f9d02814-5551-43fa-a524-51a0c801597d","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_013MpxJjFxWnKwWmmscBZnp6","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Good catch — yes, showing the user's answer to tool interactions is important for clarity.\n\nAnd yes, `assistant` is exactly the designation used in the JSONL — the `role` field is either `\"user\"` or `\"assistant\"`, and the `type` field at the top level mirrors that.\n\nSo the revised MVP output would look like:\n\n```\n## User — 12:24:03\nfor test purposes ask me a multiple choice question.\n\n## Assistant — 12:24:10\n> Tool: AskUserQuestion — \"What is the capital of France?\"\n> Answer: Paris\n\n## Assistant — 12:24:23\nCorrect! Paris is the capital of France.\n```\n\nThe tool call and its answer are grouped together under the assistant turn that initiated it, since that's where it logically belongs. Does that feel right, or would you rather show the answer on the User turn that follows?"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":3,"cache_creation_input_tokens":262,"cache_read_input_tokens":30402,"output_tokens":204,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":262,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CZTfpgcd211NoQvTgYQYK","type":"assistant","uuid":"57339a7e-66b4-450b-bf7f-3fa834ba9ff3","timestamp":"2026-03-27T13:33:17.619Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/robert.shankin/codingRepo/jsonl-reader","sessionId":"4812baa4-eab4-43d3-a58c-24d05ff631cd","version":"2.1.85","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"eager-inventing-shore"}
